# Ramos Gin Fizz

## Ingredients
* 120mL Oat Milk, Kirkland or Oatly
* 2 teaspoons Turmeric (g)
* 1 teaspoon ginger powder (g)
* 1 teaspoon cinnamon powder (g)
* 2 pinch black pepper (g)

## Procedure
Mix all ingredients in a saucepan and bring to the boil. Reduce heat, simmer for 10min on low. strain through a fine mesh strainer into mason jar, refrigerate (or serve immediately warm).
